 point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},